  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <strong>FPS horror game developed by a high school student is finally on Steam!</strong>  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1080130/extras/70271b5e8461ceacdacfc408c1bced5b.avif?t=1739655692\" width=360 height=202 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >■Dark and spooky mansion <br>An eerie monster may appear in the building <br>It is dangerous to walk around unnecessarily </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1080130/extras/edf214a17034e4d2aea5eb179fd8f797.avif?t=1739655692\" width=360 height=202 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >■ Monster appearance <br>The monsters suddenly appear <br>If you get caught even once, the game is over </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1080130/extras/c301885f1fec3bdb717632375586944d.avif?t=1739655692\" width=360 height=202 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >■ \"pursuer\" approaching  <br>A troublesome being who always follows <br>It's going to require the player to make a decision about how to stop with limited bullets.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1080130/extras/58b92c13d8ff00fa7de09c9da4379a54.avif?t=1739655692\" width=360 height=202 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >■ Collect items to avoid the crisis! <br>You can fight monsters <br>Useful weapons are falling into the building <br>Let's kill monsters with weapons! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >■ An important story begins<br>The truth which could not be told in the previous work will be revealed one after another ... <br>Watch the ending of the main character! </p>",
